      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This car is in good, reliable condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. It drives smoothly and looks great, making it a perfect choice for anyone seeking a dependable and attractive vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It's ready for its next adventure with you!",
